data.description: LIVE DOWNTOWN!   Walk to restaurants and shops!  Downtown Historic Hartselle has so much Charm and activities throughout the year!  Many Updates but still all the character of an Older Home.   Large Front Porch, Metal Roof, Vinyl Siding, Wood Floors, spacious rooms, Wood Privacy Fence in the backyard! HVAC, FLOORS, WINDOWS AND SIDING ALL JUST A FEW YEARS OLD.   ALL APPLIANCES STAY WITH THE HOUSE.   A WARM AND COZY HOME! Driving to Madison to work is less than 20 minutes and easy access with less traffic than traveling across Huntsville!   Come see this beautiful home in a very desirable community!
